---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bob Marley Tribute</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-image: url('https://www.outlooktravelmag.com/media/jamaica-tg-1024x589.png'); /* Replace with the actual URL of the background image */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .image {
            max-width: 80%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .text {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            max-width: 130%;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<Layout/>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="" alt="" class="image"> <!-- Replace with actual image URL -->
        <div class="title">MUSIC ARTIST</div>
        <div class="subtitle">BOB MARLEY</div>
        <img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/6166hXo8mpL._UF1000,1000_QL80_.jpg" alt="One Love Bob Marley" class="image"> <!-- Replace with actual image URL -->
        <div class="text">
            The artist I have chosen is Bob Marley. I like to listen to reggae songs like the artist UB40 and other reggae artists. No reggae artist can compete with Bob Marley. Bob Marley rose to fame with his backing band. Bob Marley was the best reggae artist in 1975. Bob Marley released a song "No Woman No Cry". My favourite songs from Bob Marley are "One Love" and "Buffalo Soldier".
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</Layout>
</html>
